# Summary
This documentation details the Google Analytics 4 (Web) streaming integration for Amplitude Activation, which enables forwarding Amplitude events and user data to GA4 using gtag.js. The setup requires a GA4 Measurement ID and API Secret, with options to configure event and user property mappings, including required Client ID mapping and optional User ID mapping.

